dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Rock_Addresses_2017.gdb.[The address point feature class was created to assist 911 dispatchers/calltakers in locating wireless E911 callers. Sources include: current aerial photography, NAIP aerial mosaic imagery, parcel maps, limited GPS collection and physical verification when necessary.]
